cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.HC, cs.RO 

The paper discusses the technical challenges and potential solutions for realizing the Tactile Internet over wireless networks, which involves communication, networking, and multimedia technologies. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and cs.RO (Robotics).
